Class CommonGoal10

java.lang.Object
it.polimi.ingsw.Model.Goals.CommonGoals.CommonGoal
it.polimi.ingsw.Model.Goals.CommonGoals.CommonGoal10
All Implemented Interfaces:
Serializable
public class CommonGoal10 extends CommonGoal
This class represents Common Goal number 10, which states that the goal is achieved when there are five tiles of the same color forming an X in the Bookshelf.
